===Etymology===
First attested in 1449, from {{etyl|enm|en}} {{term|abhorren|lang=enm}}, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{m|la|abhorreō||shrink away from in horror}}, from {{term|ab||from|lang=la}} + {{m|la|horreō||stand aghast, bristle with fear}}<ref>{{R:CDOE|page=2}}</ref>. Cognate with French {{term|abhorrer|lang=fr}}, {{etyl|oc|-}} {{term|aborrir|lang=oc}}.

